Company Profile
Sector: Energy
Industry: Oil, Gas & Coal
Sub-Industry: Exploration & Production
Energy XXI USA, Inc. provides oil and gas exploration services. The Company acquires, explores, and develops oil and gas fields in South Louisiana and on the Gulf of Mexico Shelf. Energy XXI serves customers in the United States.




